Roles &amp; Responsibilities

You will provide direct nursing care and ensure quality care is delivered. You will also provide guidance to patients and caregivers on the prescribed care and treatment. In addition, you will participate in quality improvement projects to improve patient care delivery.  

Requirements

 National ITE Certificate in Nursing
 Enrolled with the Singapore Nursing Board
 Good communication and interpersonal skills
 Able to perform 3 rotating shifts
 Fresh graduates are also welcome to apply 